quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  19,83,"Akuboni na ukuba Sithumele amaShayâtini (ooSathana) kwabangakholwayo, ababaphembelela ukwenza ukungcola ngempembelelo (eyenzeka rhoqo)"
  19,84,Ke wena musa ukungxama ngabo. Thina Sibabalela inani (elingephi leminyaka yokuphela kobomi babo kweli hlabathi)
  19,85,NgeMini esiya kuqokelela amalungisa kuSozinceba abe ligqiza
  19,86,Ke kaloku Siya kuqhubela abaphuli-mthetho esiHogweni benxaniwe (okweenkomo ezindilelwa emanzini ukuba ziye kusela)
  19,87,Akukho namnye oya kuba (namandla) akucenga ngaphandle kwalowo uthabathe umnqophiso kuSozinceba
  19,88,"Kananjalo bathi, “USozinceba Uthabathe (uzele) unyana.”"
  19,89,"Inene, nenze eyona nto imbi"
  19,90,"Amazulu anga angakrazuka, nomhlaba unga ungahlukana neentaba zidilike ziphasalake"
  19,91,Into yokuba babalele unyana kuSozinceba (uAllâh)
  19,92,Kodwa asinto ifanelekileyo kuSozinceba ukuba Abe nonyana
  19,93,Akukho namnye emazulwini nasemhlabeni ongazi kuSozinceba ukuba abe sisicaka (saKhe)
  19,94,"Inene (uAllâh) Wazi umntu ngamnye kubo, yaye Ubabalile ngobalo olupheleleyo"
  19,95,Yaye ngamnye kubo uya kuza kuYe (uAllâh ) eyedwa ngoMhla woVuko
  19,96,"Inene, abo bakholwayo benze izenzo zobulungisa, uSolubabalo Uya kubanika uthando"
  19,97,"Ke ngoko Thina Senze le (‘Kur’ân) yaba lula elwimini lwakho khon’ukuze unike iindaba ezivuyisayo kwabo bamoyikayo uAllâh, ulumkise kananjalo ngayo abachasi"
  19,98,Kanti zingaphi izizukulwana phambi kwabo eSazitshabalalisayo! Ingaba ungafumana nokuba mnye kuzo okanye uve nokuba kukusebeza kwabo (izizukulwana ezatshatyalaliswayo)